OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,FA doctor who treated a premature baby
OL,7,Fhas defended her decision not to
OL,8,Fadminister him with antibiotics the
OL,9,Fday before he died, an inquest heard.
OL,11,FBen Condon, who was two months old,
OL,12,Fdied at Bristol Children's Hospital in
OL,13,FApril 2015 after developing a
OL,14,Frespiratory illness.
OL,16,FDr Suzy Dean was treating Ben at the
OL,17,Fhospital's paediatric intensive care
OL,18,Funit for acute respiratory distress
OL,19,Fsyndrome (ARDS) and metapneumovirus
OL,20,F(hMPV), which is similar to the common
OL,21,Fcold in adults.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
