OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,FShe said that although Ben was being
OL,7,Fventilated and was unwell, his
OL,8,Fcondition was stable.
OL,10,FAvon Coroner's Court heard that the
OL,11,Ffollowing day, 17 April, Ben's
OL,12,Fcondition deteriorated, and he
OL,13,Fsuffered two cardiac arrests before
OL,14,Fhis death.
OL,16,FIt later emerged Ben had also
OL,17,Fdeveloped a pseudomonas bacterial
OL,18,Finfection.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
