OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,FThe University Hospitals Bristol and
OL,7,FWeston NHS Foundation Trust, which
OL,8,Fruns the children's hospital, has
OL,9,Fpreviously admitted that their failure
OL,10,Fto give Ben timely antibiotics
OL,11,Fcontributed to his death.
OL,13,FSpeaking at the inquest, Dr Dean said
OL,14,Fdoctors always recognise there is a
OL,15,Frisk of a baby developing a bacterial
OL,16,Finfection - but Ben's condition on 16
OL,17,FApril was stable.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
