OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,FAssistant Coroner Robert Sowersby
OL,7,Fasked whether there was a "missed
OL,8,Fopportunity" to test Ben's blood for a
OL,9,Fbacterial infection between 12 April
OL,10,Fand 16 April.
OL,12,F"I find that difficult because looking
OL,13,Fback on what we know now, I know there
OL,14,Fwas an infection which was unexpected,
OL,15,Fbut I don't believe he showed signs of
OL,16,Fan infection on 16 April," Dr Dean
OL,17,Freplied.
OL,19,F"I think it would have been nice to
OL,20,Fhave an extra set of bloods to
OL,21,Freassure me.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@LO]tD@AOUxD@ZO]{D@AOU
