OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1738970981
OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,F"I am not saying Ben is fine, because
OL,7,Fhe has gone ARDS, he has got
OL,8,Fsignificant ventilation requirements,
OL,9,Fand he is very much in an ICU setting.
OL,10,FBut there wasn't a paradigm shift in
OL,11,Fhow he was presenting."
OL,13,FDr Dean explained that Ben's body
OL,14,Ftemperature was fluctuating, but that
OL,15,Falone was not an indicator of an
OL,16,Finfection.
OL,18,F"To be honest, it didn't particularly
OL,19,Fconcern me, rightly or wrongly, and I
OL,20,Fappreciate the family have a strong
OL,21,Fview on that," she told the hearing.
OL,26,@sD@WO]zD@AOU}D@NO]
