OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,F"It is one factor in his care. That in
OL,7,Fitself doesn't tell me that he is
OL,8,Fdeveloping an infection."
OL,10,FDr Dean was quizzed on other signs of
OL,11,Finfection in a baby, such as rising C-
OL,12,Freactive protein levels in the blood
OL,13,Fand the "end of bed" observations.
OL,15,FBen's father, Allyn Condon, a former
OL,16,FOlympic athlete, has told the inquest
OL,17,Fthat his son was visibly deteriorating
OL,18,Fin front of him between 14 and 16
OL,19,FApril.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@YO]uD@IOUuD@TO]
