OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,FJennifer MacLeod, representing the
OL,7,FCondon family, asked Dr Dean: "That's
OL,8,Fanother indication that his infection
OL,9,Fis getting worse?"
OL,11,F'I didn't feel he was changing' -
OL,12,Fdoctor at inquest
OL,14,FThe witness replied: "Yes it would be,
OL,15,Fbut the difficulty is that I didn't
OL,16,Fshare that view that he was changing
OL,17,Fthat significantly from the end of the
OL,18,Fbed.
OL,26,@oD@_OUqD@RO]vD@VOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
