OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1738970981
OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,F"We had fluctuations in the amount of
OL,7,Ffluid he was carrying, and you can see
OL,8,Fslightly puffy eyes and there were a
OL,9,Ffew periods where the diuretics were
OL,10,Fincreased just to try and manage that.
OL,12,F"It's what's expected and not expected
OL,13,Fin terms of his colour, how he handles
OL,14,Fand responds to being touched and
OL,15,Fmoved.
OL,17,F"How does to look to me? Is he warm?
OL,18,FIs he cold? That's the sort of
OL,19,Fsubtlety you only get by touching and
OL,20,Fthat is difficult to get across in the
OL,21,Fnotes. I didn't feel he was changing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
