OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,FMs MacLeod suggested Ben was getting
OL,7,Fworse the day before he died because
OL,8,Fof a bacterial infection.
OL,10,F"I don't agree with that," Dr Dean
OL,11,Fsaid. "There are other markers that we
OL,12,Fhave not talked about as well.
OL,14,F"Two other consultants examined him on
OL,15,Fthe afternoon of April 16 and neither
OL,16,Fof them felt anything else needed to
OL,17,Fbe changed, it's not just my view on
OL,18,Fthat day.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@ZO]sD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
