PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1738970981
OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,F"He didn't look unwell from the end of
OL,7,Fthe bed, and I appreciate his family
OL,8,Ffeel otherwise. That was just my view
OL,9,Fat the time.
OL,11,F"The thing about paediatric intensive
OL,12,Fcare is that Ben was actually quite a
OL,13,Fstable patient in that he wasn't doing
OL,14,Fanything that I didn't expect.
OL,16,F"Yes, he had ARDS, and yes, his
OL,17,Fventilation was getting worse, not
OL,18,Fbetter. But he was stable around that.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
