PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1738970981
OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,F"Someone of Ben's age is not going to
OL,7,Flook stable if they have got sepsis,
OL,8,Fit just doesn't look like that.
OL,10,F"Regardless of what I saw and thought,
OL,11,FI did have two other colleagues look
OL,12,Fat him that day. Three of us were not
OL,13,Fconcerned that we needed to escalate
OL,14,Fhis treatment."
OL,16,FDr Dean told the court she had
OL,17,Freflected on whether the antibiotics
OL,18,Fshould have been administered sooner.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
