CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1738970981
OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,F"I know what I did on that day is
OL,7,Fdifferent to what some of the experts
OL,8,Fhave suggested, for example," she said.
OL,10,F"But I think, and I know I keep saying
OL,11,Fthat every child is at risk of
OL,12,Fsecondary infection, but if we treated
OL,13,Fevery child that had a change of x-ray
OL,14,Fand the changes we saw in Ben with
OL,15,Fantibiotics, then we would be treating
OL,16,Fwith antibiotics all the time and
OL,17,Fthat's just not the right thing to do.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@]O]rD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
