PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1738970981
OL,3,CDoctor defends decision not to give
OL,4,Cantibiotics to baby who later died
OL,6,F"We have to rely on what we are seeing
OL,7,Fand if things change, reassess. You
OL,8,Fcannot put someone on antibiotics
OL,9,Fbecause there is a risk of it, because
OL,10,Fevery child is at risk of it."
OL,12,FThe inquest continues.
